name: Math.seal()
body:
### Math.seal(n {, audioContext})

#### Arguements
1. `n`: a number to round to the nearest 5341
2. `audioContext`: an AudioContext to stream seal into

Returns `5341`

#### Usage
```javascript
require('math-seal')
var context = new AudioContext()
Math.seal(123, context) // => 5341
```
